              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "para-0-1",
          "content": "In 2025, The Browser Company revived the phrase amid its pivot from the Arc browser to the AI-focused Dia, signaling webpages yielding to AI chat interfaces that search, generate, and call APIs.CEO Josh Miller's letter to Arc members invoked 2019 trends like cloud surges and WebAssembly, while crowdsourcing Arc's community-led future.This evolution underscores browsers as hubs for workflows from design to enterprise SaaS.",
