                  "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=rsrch.space&sz=32",
                  "title": "Meet us in the browser"
                },
                {
                  "id": "source-9",
                  "name": "mjtsai",
                  "url": "https://mjtsai.com/blog/2025/05/",
                  "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=mjtsai.com&sz=32",
                  "title": "Meet us in the browser"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "para-1-1",
          "content": "Figma's growth reflected broader adoption, with 87% of new users joining via colleagues and Community enabling file remixing.The platform evolved beyond multiplayer to bridge engineering and design, creating reusable components and brand assets.This approach positioned Figma as a scalable system, making design skills as ubiquitous as Google Docs proficiency.",
