    {
      "id": "section-2",
      "title": "Arc-to-Dia Pivot Revives Mantra Amid AI Browser Trends",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "para-2-0",
          "content": "The Browser Company's January 2025 letter by Josh Miller echoed Figma's ethos, announcing no new Arc features while prioritizing Dia's AI interfaces over traditional webpages.Analyst Michael Tsai critiqued the pivot's equivocation, predicting Arc's end despite denials, but lauded Dia's context-aware quizzing from tabs and history.This shift aligns with browsers hosting entire workflows, from crypto extensions to SaaS.",
          "citations": [
